videos.description: Tre Jones turns the ball over, and the Hokies get out and running, as Ahmed Hill passes to Nickeil Alexander-Walker for the layup.
videos.headline: Alexander-Walker scores off Duke turnover

videos.description: RJ Barrett lofts one up through three white jerseys and is able to sink the shot for Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Barrett floats one over 3 Virginia Tech defenders) 2019/02/26

videos.headline: Barrett floats one over 3 Virginia Tech defenders

videos.description: Cam Reddish is whistled for the charge and to add insult to injury lands hard on the court.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Reddish slow to get up after hard fall) 2019/02/26

videos.headline: Reddish slow to get up after hard fall

videos.description: Jack White makes up for a turnover with a nice stop on defense, and RJ Barrett goes the other way for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (White's defense sets up Barrett's layup) 2019/02/26

videos.headline: White's defense sets up Barrett's layup

videos.description: RJ Barrett starts to heat up with a triple, and Zion Williamson loves it from the bench.
videos.headline: Zion pumped after Barrett's 3-pointer

videos.description: Kerry Blackshear Jr. gets the ball in the post, and goes straight at Javin DeLaurier.
videos.headline: Blackshear scores and-1 layup

videos.description: Kerry Blackshear Jr. fakes out Cam Reddish, then rises for the big jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Blackshear gets Reddish in the air, then dunks it down) 2019/02/26

videos.headline: Blackshear gets Reddish in the air, then dunks it down

videos.description: Wabissa Bede finds Ty Outlaw in the corner and he hits the 3-pointer to break a tie with 1:30 left in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Outlaw hits big trey for Hokies) 2019/02/26

videos.headline: Outlaw hits big trey for Hokies

videos.description: Ty Outlaw hits a big 3-pointer down the stretch and the No. 20 Hokies defeat the No. 3 Blue Devils 77-72.
